BFGMiner is a modular ASIC/FPGA miner written in C, featuring dynamic
clocking, monitoring, and fanspeed support for bitcoin and derivative
coins. This is a fork with FreeBSD compatibility patches.

Features:
- Support for multiple mining devices (ASIC, FPGA, GPU, CPU)
- Stratum and getwork protocol support
- Multiple blockchain/pool support
- Dynamic clocking and monitoring
- Remote API interface
